@baseUrl = http://localhost:5079

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/Event
Accept: application/json

###

### Get event by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/Event/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create event
POST {{baseUrl}}/Event
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "E-Sports Finals",
  "location": "Rotterdam Ahoy",
  "date": "2025-01-01T18:00:00",
  "description": "Big LAN event",
  "detail": "16 pro teams competing",
  "status": "Upcoming",
  "imageUrl": null
}

###

### Update existing event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Event/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "E-Sports Finals - Updated",
  "location": "Rotterdam Ahoy",
  "date": "2025-01-02T18:00:00",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "detail": "Now 20 teams competing",
  "status": "Updated",
  "imageUrl": null
}

###

### Delete event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Event/1
Accept: application/json
